source/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}, {\"begin\": 1610, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999982659318476, \"rank\": 1.734071193181631e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1490}, {\"ngram\": \"the championships\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the desired result\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1553}, {\"ngram\": \"their place\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1585}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1606}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can only wish for the best because we would have written to all the agents and coaches, both locally and internationally, and those in the collegiate system as well who are performing very well,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1826, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the agents\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"the collegiate system\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are looking forward to putting the available team into competition so that we can get that team qualified for the Paris Olympics,\\\" Gayle stated.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1975, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1962, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9999990795501761, \"rank\": 9.20450569837967e-07, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the available team\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"that team\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1959}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted that patience is necessary with the country's athletes because most of them have had a very long season and they have always put their best foot forward whenever they are called to represent Jamaica.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2183, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999804284328407, \"rank\": 1.956988203198261e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"patience\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's athletes\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"a very long season\", \"from\": 2077, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"their best foot\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I must also indicate that we must be patient because while we wish for the best and always want to have our teams doing well, there are also times when we will just not be able to field the best of teams.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our teams\", \"from\": 2298, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we seek to do our best for our athletes and for the country,\\\" Gayle asserted.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"score\": 0.9999990795501761, \"rank\": 9.20450569837967e-07, \"text\": \"Gayle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Gayle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2442}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\